                    java.time.LocalDateTime lastUpdate,
                    java.lang.String lastUpdatedBy,
                    int customerID,
                    int userID)
        Constructor for the Appointment Class. This will assign default values to the Appointment values.
        Parameters:
        appointmentID - the appointment id
        title - the appointment title
        description - the appointment description
        location - the appointment location
        contactID - the contact ID associated with the appointment
        type - the appointment type
        startDate - the appointment start date
        startTime - the appointment start time
        startDateTime - the appointment combined start date and time
        endDate - the appointment end date
        endTime - the appointment end time
        endDateTime - the appointment combined end date and time
        createDate - the date and time the appointment was created
        createdBy - the user that created the appointment
        lastUpdate - that date and time the appointment was most recently updated
        lastUpdatedBy - the user that last updated the appointment
        customerID - the customer ID that is associated with the appointment
        userID - the user ID that is associated with the appointment
